title: Create a collectible nft game
body:
People can buy random packages of NFT for a ticket or some set amount of cake, these packages can contain an example of 10 or 15 collectibles, which people can then sell in another places, the idea would be for there between 3 and 6 months to generate a new collection and with each package sold from PancakeSwap, you can use these to burn cakes and reduce inflation.

Having a complete collection can give people access to a pool with higher APY benefits for their savings or to obtain future benefits from the platform.
choices: Bad idea, may be in another time
